import { useState } from "react"; import "./PresetManager.scss"; const PresetManager = (props) => { const [cur_preset, setCurPreset] = useState("wheat") const topics = [ {key: "key", name: "Ключ шаблона", type: "text"}, {key: "name", name: "Имя шаблона", type: "text"}, {key: "line_spacing", name: "Расстояние между линиями", type: "number", min: 1, max: 10, step: 1}, {key: "speed", name: "Скорость перемещения", type: "number", min: 0.1, max: 30, step: 0.1}, {key: "alt", name: "Высота полета", type: "number", min: 1, max: 10, step: 0.1}, {key: "mode", name: "Режим опрыскивателя", type: "select", option_names: ["Струя", "Спрей"], option_values: ["jet", "spray"]}, {key: "liters_per_hectar", name: "Литров на гектар", type: "number", min: 1, max: 300, step: 1}, ] return
} export default PresetManager
